OL,3,CKing and Queen to attend series of
OL,4,Cevents in Scotland as Royal Week begins
OL,6,FThe King and Queen are preparing for a
OL,7,Fseries of engagements north of the
OL,8,Fborder as Royal Week gets under way in
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,FCharles will begin his official
OL,12,Fengagements by receiving a Royal
OL,13,FSalute and inspecting a guard of
OL,14,Fhonour provided by Balaklava Company,
OL,15,F5th Battalion Royal Regiment of
OL,16,FScotland, in the gardens of the Palace
OL,17,Fof Holyroodhouse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
