PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782719281
OL,3,CKing and Queen to attend series of
OL,4,Cevents in Scotland as Royal Week begins
OL,6,FHe will then be formally welcomed to
OL,7,Fthe Scottish capital with the Ceremony
OL,8,Fof the Keys, in which Lord Provost
OL,9,FRobert Aldridge will present the keys
OL,10,Fto the City of Edinburgh to the King,
OL,11,Fwho will return them for safe keeping.
OL,13,FThe King will also preside over an
OL,14,Finvestiture ceremony at the Palace of
OL,15,FHolyroodhouse on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
