CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782719281
OL,3,CKing and Queen to attend series of
OL,4,Cevents in Scotland as Royal Week begins
OL,6,FThose receiving honours will include
OL,7,Fforensic scientist Lorna Dawson, who
OL,8,Fwas awarded a damehood in the New Year
OL,9,FHonours, and New Seekers singer Eve
OL,10,FGraham, who becomes an MBE for
OL,11,Fservices to the music industry.
OL,13,FSimon Milne, regius keeper of the
OL,14,FRoyal Botanic Garden Edinburgh, also
OL,15,Freceives a knighthood for services to
OL,16,Fbotany, conservation and horticulture.
OL,18,FLater on Tuesday, the King and Queen
OL,19,Fwill host guests at a garden party at
OL,20,Fthe palace, alongside the Duke of
OL,21,FEdinburgh and the Princess Royal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
