OL,3,CKing and Queen to attend series of
OL,4,Cevents in Scotland as Royal Week begins
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the King and Queen will
OL,7,Fattend the Order of the Thistle
OL,8,Fservice at St Giles Cathedral in
OL,9,FEdinburgh, together with the Duke of
OL,10,FRothesay and the Duke of Edinburgh.
OL,12,FThe following day, the King will visit
OL,13,FJedburgh in the Scottish Borders,
OL,14,Fwhere he will view a procession taking
OL,15,Fplace as part of the town's Jethart
OL,16,FCallant festival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
