FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782719281
OL,3,CKing and Queen to attend series of
OL,4,Cevents in Scotland as Royal Week begins
OL,6,FDuring the visit, he will also be
OL,7,Finvited to start the annual game of
OL,8,Fhand ba', a street sport that has been
OL,9,Fplayed in the town each year since
OL,10,F1704.
OL,12,FThe monarch traditionally spends a
OL,13,Fweek based at the Palace of
OL,14,FHolyroodhouse each year in what is
OL,15,Fknown as Holyrood Week or Royal Week
OL,16,Fin Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
